description: This file is the entry point for a React application. It imports React, ReactDOM, a CSS stylesheet, and the main App component. It then creates a root element in the DOM and renders the App component within React.StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root element for rendering the React application into a DOM node.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM.
